---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Deep Dummying">
  <div class="container--narrow">
    <div class="about-wrap">

      <div class="about-eyebrow">
        <span class="mono-label">about</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="about-title">;DD</h1>
      <p class="about-subtitle">Deep Dummying</p>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>What is this?</h2>
        <p>
          Deep Dummying is a personal lab and living document. It's where I build things
          that are too low-level to matter commercially and too interesting to ignore —
          kernels, allocators, protocol clients, debuggers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every project here is documented from the ground up: not just the final result,
          but the steps, the wrong turns, the experiments, and the questions I haven't
          answered yet. It's less of a portfolio and more of a running log of understanding.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          Most of programming is building on top of abstractions you don't understand.
          That works fine until it doesn't — until something breaks in a way that only
          makes sense if you know what's underneath.
        </p>
        <p>
          The point of going low-level isn't to reinvent everything from scratch.
          It's to develop the kind of intuition that makes you a better programmer
          at every level of the stack. When you've written a memory allocator,
          you think about heap allocations differently. When you've traced a syscall
          all the way into the kernel, you stop treating the OS as magic.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site is built around one conviction: <strong>understanding compounds.</strong>
          Every concept you actually internalize makes the next one faster to learn.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>What's here</h2>
        <div class="about-map">
          <div class="about-map__item">
            <span class="tag tag--project">projects</span>
            <p>Long-form project documentation, written chapter by chapter as the project develops. Source code, design decisions, and things that went wrong.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-map__item">
            <span class="tag tag--concept">concepts</span>
            <p>Deep dives into systems concepts — virtual memory, scheduling, ELF, cache coherence. Written as I learn them, updated as my understanding improves.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-map__item">
            <span class="tag tag--experiment">experiments</span>
            <p>Small, focused investigations with a hypothesis and a result. Sometimes they confirm what I expected. Often they don't.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-map__item">
            <span class="tag tag--resource">resources</span>
            <p>Books, papers, and references that actually helped — with notes on what to read and why.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Who</h2>
        <p>
          I'm Saeed. I spend most of my time reading kernel source, poking at binaries,
          and building things in C that probably already exist but are more fun to write myself.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>
          and deployed on Vercel. All content is written in Markdown. The design is intentionally minimal —
          the less the UI competes for attention, the more room there is for the ideas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-contact">
        <div class="about-contact__inner">
          <div class="about-contact__text">
            <p class="about-contact__label">Come talk</p>
            <p class="about-contact__desc">
              If you're building something low-level, stuck on a concept, or just want
              to talk systems — the Discord is open.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="https://discord.gg/YOUR_INVITE"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="about-discord-btn"
          >
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057 19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03z"/>
            </svg>
            Join the Discord
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-footer-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/saeeedhany" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-link">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          github.com/saeeedhany
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
.about-wrap {
  padding: 4rem 0 8rem;
  max-width: 58ch;
}

.about-eyebrow {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.mono-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

.about-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.about-subtitle {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}

.about-section {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  padding-bottom: 3rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.about-section h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.about-section p {
  color: var(--text-dim);
  line-height: 1.85;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-size: 0.97rem;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.about-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.about-section strong {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.about-section a {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-hover);
}
.about-section a:hover {
  color: var(--text);
  border-color: var(--accent);
}

.about-map {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.25rem;
}

.about-map__item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.about-map__item .tag {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 0.1rem;
}

.about-map__item p {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Discord contact box */
.about-contact {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.about-contact__inner {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 2rem;
  padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-1);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.about-contact__label {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.about-contact__desc {
  font-size: 0.83rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
  max-width: 36ch;
  margin: 0;
}

.about-discord-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
  background: #5865F2;
  color: #fff;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 0.83rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;
  transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.about-discord-btn:hover {
  opacity: 0.88;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  color: #fff;
}

.about-footer-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.about-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.about-link:hover { color: var(--text); }
</style>
